    <item>
      <title>瑞银获得资本计划支持，埃尔莫蒂获得挪威财富基金的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ubs-gets-backing-capital-plan-ermotti-pay-norway-wealth-fund-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威主权财富基金支持瑞银计划，通过保护投资者免遭破产，使其额外一级债券（AT1）债券（一种债务形式）对投资者更具吸引力，并签署了瑞银首席执行官塞尔吉奥·埃尔莫蒂（Sergio Ermotti）的薪酬方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ubs-gets-backing-capital-plan-ermotti-pay-norway-wealth-fund-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 08:47:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊计划今年提前偿还欧元区救助贷款--消息人士</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/greece-plans-early-repayment-eurozone-bailout-loans-this-year-sources-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名政府官员周二对路透社表示，希腊计划今年提前偿还向欧元区国家提供的高达 50 亿欧元（53.4 亿美元）的救助贷款，以寻求在过去十年的债务危机后恢复正常。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/greece-plans-early-repayment-eurozone-bailout-loans-this-year-sources-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 08:17:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
